Package com.streambase.sbunit.ext.matchers

Interface Summary
IgnoreNullTransform This interface is used to control structural recursion of ValueMatchers when creating a new version of them that ignores nulls values.
 

Class Summary
AnythingMatcher A TupleMatcher and a ValueMatcher that always matches.
FieldBasedTupleMatcher FieldBasedTupleMatcher matches tuples by comparing their fields against ValueMatchers.
NothingMatcher A TupleMatcher and a ValueMatcher that never matches.
